query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(a1 q1 s t1 tq1 u1) NoHashJoin(a1 acc q1 s t1 tq1 u1 b) */ select acc.location,
count(*)
from question AS q1
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.view_count >= 100 AND q1.view_count <= 100000
inner join tag AS t1
on t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('build',
'counter',
'css-float',
'datetime',
'firefox',
'google-plus',
'inline',
'itunesconnect',
'lisp',
'momentjs',
'ruby-on-rails-3.1',
'thumbnails',
'visual-studio',
'yaml')
inner join answer AS a1
on q1.id = a1.question_id
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND s.site_id = a1.site_id AND s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow',
'superuser')
inner join so_user AS u1
on s.site_id = u1.site_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND u1.reputation >= 0 AND u1.reputation <= 100
inner join account AS acc
on acc.id = u1.account_id
inner join badge AS b
on s.site_id = b.site_id AND b.user_id = u1.id AND b.name IN ('Analytical',
'Announcer',
'Benefactor',
'Cleanup',
'Disciplined',
'Documentation User',
'Fanatic',
'Investor',
'Nice Answer',
'Not a Robot',
'Organizer',
'Suffrage',
'Tag Editor',
'Talkative',
'Vox Populi') group by acc.location order by count(*) desc LIMIT 100;
